        "subject": "=Upcoming Milestone Deadline: {{$json.milestone_title}}\n\n",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;\">\n\n  <p>\n    Dear {{$json.milestone_owner_firstname}} {{$json.milestone_owner_lastname}},\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    This is a reminder that the milestone <strong>{{$json.milestone_title}}</strong> is scheduled to reach its planned completion in <strong>3 days</strong>.\n  </p>\n\n  <h3 style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Milestone Details</h3>\n\n  <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 600px;\">\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Milestone Name</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.milestone_title}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Project Name</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.project_title}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Start Date</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.milestone_start_date}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Planned End Date</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.milestone_end_date}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Milestone Link</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n        <a href=\"https://fm-matrix.lockated.com/vas/projects/{{$json.project_id}}/milestones/{{$json.milestone_id}}\" target=\"_blank\">\n          View Milestone Details\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n\n  </table>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n    We recommend reviewing the progress of associated tasks and addressing any potential risks to ensure timely completion.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Please take necessary action to keep the milestone on track.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Regards,<br>\n    <strong>Project Management Office</strong>\n  </p>\n\n</div>",
